quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  30,42,"Maaku: "Yiilee ka leydi, ndaaron ko honno battane adinoo…ďe …ďen wa'anoo. Tawno ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe ko sirkoo…ďe"."
  30,43,"Feewtinir ye'eso maa ngon e diina po'occii…óa kan, ado √Īalaande arde immorde ka Alla nde ruttetaake. Nde √Īalnde, …ďe seeday:"
  30,44,"Kala jeddu…óo, haray geddi makko …óin no fawii mo. Kala non gollu…óo mo∆ī∆īere, haray ko ko'e-ma…ď…ďe …ďe kebilani (Aljanna),"
  30,45,"fii yo O yo…ď …ďeen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe ngolli mo∆ī∆īu…ói, e …ďural makko ngal. KaŇčko On, O yi…óaa he'efer…ďe …ďen."
  30,46,"Hino jeyaa e Ma'andeeji makko …óin: Wurtugol Mo keneeli …óin wewlinooji, e fii yo O mee…óin on e yurmeende makko nden, e no laa…óe …óen dogira e yamiroore makko, e fii yo o …óa…ď…ďu e …ďural makko. Mbelajo'o, on njettat[Mo]."
  30,47,"GooŇč…óii Min nulii ado maa…óa Nulaa…ďe haa e yim…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, …ďe addani …ďe …ďanngannduyeeji. Min njottii e …ďen bonnu…ďe; tawi no jojji e Amen paabagol gooŇč…óii…ďe …ďen."
  30,48,"Ko Alla woni nuloowo kenee…ói …óin, …ói cogga duule …óen; O saakitira …óuum ka weeyo no o yi…óiri; O wa…óta …óuum ta∆īe-ta∆īe. A yi'ay to…ďo ngon no yalta hakkude mun. Si O heewtinii ngo e on mo o muuyi e jeyaa…ďe makko …ďen, e jaka kam…ďe he…ďe weltoo."
  30,49,"GooŇč…óii …ďe laatinoke ado (to…ďo) ngon jippineede e ma…ď…ďe, ko ta∆īinoo…ďe."
  30,50,"Ndaarii e battane yurmeende Alla nden, no o wuurnitorta leydi …ďaawo ndi yoorude. Pellet, wa…óoowo …óuum On, ko guurnitoowo maay…ďe …ďen, KaŇčko Ko O kattan…óo kala hu'unde."